    • demandBooks

      public boolean demandBooks​(Publication demandedBook)
      Demands to add the specified book to the library stock. If the book is already in the stock, does nothing. If the book is not in the stock, it adds it to the demanded books list of the library.
      Parameters:
      demandedBook - is the book that will be demanded.
      Returns:
      true if the book is added to the demanded books list, false if not.

    • demandBookStock

      bookLanguage - language of book.
      Returns:
      the amount of the book in the library stock.

    • lendBook

      public Publication lendBook​(Publication givenBook, StandartReader reader)
      Lends a book to a customer. If the book is not in the stock demands the book. If the book is in the stock, successfuly lends the book to the customer.
      Parameters:
      givenBook - is the book that will be lend.
      reader - standart reader.
      Returns:
      the Book that is lend, null if no books is lend.

    • relendBook

      public boolean relendBook​(Publication returnedBook, StandartReader customer)
      Relends a book from a costumer. Adds the returned book to the library stock. If the book is not in borrowedBooks section of the customer then does not do anything.
      Parameters:
      returnedBook - returned book object.
      customer - standart reader.
      Returns:
      true if relend is done, false if not.

    • searchBook

      Parameters:

      bookLanguage - language of book.
      Returns:
      true if the book is found in the stock, false if not.
